metadata.quality_notes: Complete dataset with auto-generated news URLs. All entries require manual verification of news URLs and AI tag pages.
migration_notes: Migrated to schema v3.0.0 on 2025-11-04: Converted news_sources to array structure, removed broken ai_tag_url field, added multi-source support for AI research institutions
